00:02:45.719 --> 00:02:47.639
If not, he'd beat me again.

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:53.560
Don't worry.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:54.479
I've promised you

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:56.719
that I'll always protect you.

